#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reduce the number of #includes in &kde; source files"
msgstr "Redueix el nombre de #includes en els fitxers font del &kde;"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> <group><option>-v, --verbose</option></group> "
"<group><option>-e, --experimental</option></group> <group><option>-m, --"
"modify</option></group> <group><option><replaceable>file</replaceable></"
"option></group> <group><option>--help</option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> <group><option>-v, --verbose</option></group> "
"<group><option>-e, --experimental</option></group> <group><option>-m, --"
"modify</option></group> <group><option><replaceable>fitxer</replaceable></"
"option></group> <group><option>--help</option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descripció"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> tries to reduce the number of #includes in C+"
"+ source files. Much of it's processing is specific to &kde; sources and so "
"it might not work so well with sources for non-&kde; applications."
msgstr ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> intenta reduir el nombre de #includes en els "
"fitxers de codi font de C++. La majoria del processament que realitza és "
"específic per a &kde; i per això és possible que no funcioni tan bé sobre "
"fonts d'aplicacions no &kde;."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following problems are identified by <command>fixincludes</command>:"
msgstr ""
"Els següents problemes són identificats per <command>fixincludes</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Including headers that are no longer supported but which exist for "
"compatibility with older Qt/KDE versions;"
msgstr ""
"Incloure capçaleres que ja no estan suportades però que existeixen per "
"compatibilitat amb antigues versions de Qt/KDE;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Including the same file multiple times."
msgstr "Incloure el mateix fitxer múltiples vegades."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also an experimental mode which tries removing each #include one at "
"a time (with a few exceptions) to see whether the source still compiles. "
"Note that this experimental mode will modify the original sources."
msgstr ""
"També disposa d'un mode experimental que intenta eliminar un #include cada "
"vegada (amb algunes excepcions) per a comprovar si el codi segueix "
"compilant. Tingueu present que això modifica el codi font original."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default the sources will not be modified; the identified problems will "
"simply be written to standard output."
msgstr ""
"Per omissió, no es modifiquen els fitxers originals, simplement s'escriuen a "
"l'eixida estàndard."

# skip-rule: punctuation-period-no
#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of C++ sources to examine should be given on the command-line. If "
"no files are given, all C++ sources in or beneath the current directory will "
"be examined (with the exception of directories whose <filename>Makefile.am</"
"filename> contains <option>-UQT_NO_COMPAT</option> or <option>-"
"UKDE_NO_COMPAT</option>)"
msgstr ""
"La llista de fitxers de C++ a analitzar haurà de ser indicada mitjançant la "
"línia d'ordres. Si no s'indica cap fitxer, s'examinaran els del directori "
"actual junt amb els seus subdirectoris (menys els que en el seu fitxer "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename> contingui les opcions <option>-"
"UQT_NO_COMPAT</option> o <option>-UKDE_NO_COMPAT</option>)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the KDE Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta utilitat forma part del joc de desenvolupament de programari del "
"&kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opcions"

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --verbose"
msgstr "-v, --verbose"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Verbose mode. Additional debugging output is written to standard output."
msgstr ""
"Mode informatiu. Mostra informació de depuració addicional escrivint-la a "
"l'eixida estàndard."

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "-e, --experimental"
msgstr "-e, --experimental"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Experimental mode, as described above in detail. Note that this option "
"implies <option>--modify</option>."
msgstr ""
"Mode experimental, ja ha estat descrit amb detall abans. Tingueu present que "
"aquesta opció implica <option>--modify</option>."

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "-m, --modify"
msgstr "-m, --modify"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As well as writing messages to standard output, actually modify the original "
"sources to fix any problems that were found."
msgstr ""
"Alhora que escriu els missatges a través de l'eixida estàndard, es modifica "
"el codi original per a solucionar qualsevol problema trobat."

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "Autors"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> was written by Dirk Mueller "
"<email>mueller@kde.org</email>."
msgstr ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> ha estat escrit per en Dirk Mueller "
"<email>mueller@kde.org</email>."

